Package org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtistsManager
    Manager responsible for keep in memory the details of the existing artist on the disk.
    MusicArtistFactory
    Contains handy method for create music artist artists, loading the details from the disk and for save those to the disk.
    MusicArtistFactory.Reader
    The class responsible for read the artist details from file, parse those and create a valid artist.
    MusicArtistFactory.Writer
    The class responsible for write the artist details to file.
    MusicArtistObservableFileWrapper
    This entity encapsulate a MusicArtist in order to detect changes of the artist when it is reinitialize via MusicArtistObservableFileWrapper.set(MusicArtist) (changes to the instance of artist is listen too since it implements the Observable interface.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MusicArtistFactory.MusicArtistType
    Type of music artist.
